c: 65
v: 6
t: "(Abo bagore bategereje igihe cyabo cya Eda) mujye mubarekera aho mutuye bijyanye n’ubushobozi bwanyu. Ntimukanabatoteze mugamije kubabuza amahwemo (kugira ngo babavire mu ngo). Nibaba batwite, mujye mubaha ibibatunga kugeza babyaye. Nibabonkereza (bakabasaba igihembo) mujye mubaha ibihembo byabo, kandi mujye mubijyaho inama ku neza. Ariko nimutumvikana, undi (mugore) yamumwonkereza"